    <briefdescription>
<para>Cooperative scheduler for protothread tasks. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The scheduler manages an array of <ref refid="structSYN__Task" kindref="compound">SYN_Task</ref> descriptors. On each tick it selects the highest-priority ready task and calls its protothread function. Equal-priority tasks are served round-robin.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structSYN__Task" kindref="compound">SYN_Task</ref><sp/>tasks[3];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structSYN__Sched" kindref="compound">SYN_Sched</ref><sp/>sched;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sched_8c_1a240a64b7dba2fe25491ba9512c3b6056" kindref="member">syn_task_create</ref>(&amp;tasks[0],<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;blink&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/><sp/><sp/>blink_fn,<sp/><sp/><sp/>1,<sp/>NULL);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sched_8c_1a240a64b7dba2fe25491ba9512c3b6056" kindref="member">syn_task_create</ref>(&amp;tasks[1],<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;serial&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/><sp/>serial_fn,<sp/><sp/>0,<sp/>NULL);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sched_8c_1a240a64b7dba2fe25491ba9512c3b6056" kindref="member">syn_task_create</ref>(&amp;tasks[2],<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;monitor&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>monitor_fn,<sp/>2,<sp/>NULL);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sched_8c_1adce0587af91fb3565da52684541f0582" kindref="member">syn_sched_init</ref>(&amp;sched,<sp/>tasks,<sp/>3);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__sched_8c_1a72ea4ec9b0d0f3d478b83238b9ce6989" kindref="member">syn_sched_run_forever</ref>(&amp;sched);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
